          "answer": "समीकरणों को मानक रूप में लिखने पर:<br>2x + 5y - 1 = 0  (a1=2, b1=5, c1=-1)<br>2x + 3y - 3 = 0  (a2=2, b2=3, c2=-3)<br>वज्र-गुणन सूत्र: x / (b1c2 - b2c1) = y / (c1a2 - c2a1) = 1 / (a1b2 - a2b1)<br>=> x / ((5)(-3) - (3)(-1)) = y / ((-1)(2) - (-3)(2)) = 1 / ((2)(3) - (2)(5))<br>=> x / (-15 + 3) = y / (-2 + 6) = 1 / (6 - 10)<br>=> <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">x</span><span class=\"den\">-12</span></span> = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">y</span><span class=\"den\">4</span></span> = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">1</span><span class=\"den\">-4</span></span><br>x के लिए: <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">x</span><span class=\"den\">-12</span></span> = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">1</span><span class=\"den\">-4</span></span> => x = -<span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">12</span><span class=\"den\">-4</span></span> = 3<br>y के लिए: <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">y</span><span class=\"den\">4</span></span> = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">1</span><span class=\"den\">-4</span></span> => y = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">4</span><span class=\"den\">-4</span></span> = -1<br>अतः x = 3 और y = -1. Ans."
