          "answer": "दिया गया हल x = 1 और y = 3 है।<br>समीकरण (i) में x और y का मान रखने पर:<br>2(1) + k(3) = 3<br>=> 2 + 3k = 3 => 3k = 1 => k = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">1</span><span class=\"den\">3</span></span><br>समीकरण (ii) में x और y का मान रखने पर:<br>1 - h(3) = 2<br>=> 1 - 3h = 2 => -3h = 1 => h = -<span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">1</span><span class=\"den\">3</span></span><br>अतः h = -<span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">1</span><span class=\"den\">3</span></span> और k = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">1</span><span class=\"den\">3</span></span>. Ans."
