          "question": "किसी संख्या और उसके व्युत्क्रम (reciprocal) का योग <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">10</span><span class=\"den\">3</span></span> है। संख्या ज्ञात करें। [15 (A) II, 16 (A) II, 22 (A) I]",
          "answer": "माना वह संख्या = x<br>तब उसका व्युत्क्रम = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">1</span><span class=\"den\">x</span></span><br>प्रश्नानुसार:<br>x + <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">1</span><span class=\"den\">x</span></span> = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">10</span><span class=\"den\">3</span></span><br>=> (x² + 1) / x = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">10</span><span class=\"den\">3</span></span><br>वज्र-गुणन (Cross multiply) करने पर:<br>=> 3(x² + 1) = 10x<br>=> 3x² + 3 = 10x<br>=> 3x² - 10x + 3 = 0<br>गुणनखंड करने पर:<br>=> 3x² - 9x - x + 3 = 0<br>=> 3x(x - 3) - 1(x - 3) = 0<br>=> (3x - 1)(x - 3) = 0<br>=> 3x - 1 = 0  => x = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">1</span><span class=\"den\">3</span></span><br>या x - 3 = 0  => x = 3<br>अतः अभीष्ट संख्या 3 या <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">1</span><span class=\"den\">3</span></span> है। Ans."
