          "answer": "थेल्स प्रमेय (आधारभूत आनुपातिकता प्रमेय) से, यदि DE || BC हो, तो:<br><span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">AD</span><span class=\"den\">DB</span></span> = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">AE</span><span class=\"den\">EC</span></span><br>मान रखने पर:<br><span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">4x - 3</span><span class=\"den\">3x - 1</span></span> = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">8x - 7</span><span class=\"den\">5x - 3</span></span><br>वज्र-गुणन करने पर:<br>(4x - 3)(5x - 3) = (8x - 7)(3x - 1)<br>20x² - 12x - 15x + 9 = 24x² - 8x - 21x + 7<br>20x² - 27x + 9 = 24x² - 29x + 7<br>सभी पदों को एक तरफ ले जाने पर:<br>24x² - 20x² - 29x + 27x + 7 - 9 = 0<br>4x² - 2x - 2 = 0<br>2 से भाग देने पर:<br>2x² - x - 1 = 0<br>गुणनखंड: 2x² - 2x + x - 1 = 0<br>2x(x - 1) + 1(x - 1) = 0<br>(2x + 1)(x - 1) = 0<br>x = -<span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">1</span><span class=\"den\">2</span></span> (जो संभव नहीं है क्योंकि दूरी ऋणात्मक नहीं होती)<br>अतः x = 1. Ans."
