          "answer": "यहाँ x1 = 2, y1 = -2 ; x2 = -7, y2 = 4<br>अनुपात m1 = 1, m2 = 3<br>विभाजन सूत्र (Section Formula) से:<br>x = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">m1.x2 + m2.x1</span><span class=\"den\">m1 + m2</span></span><br>x = (1×(-7) + 3×2) / (1 + 3) = (-7 + 6) / 4 = -<span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">1</span><span class=\"den\">4</span></span><br>y = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">m1.y2 + m2.y1</span><span class=\"den\">m1 + m2</span></span><br>y = (1×4 + 3×(-2)) / (1 + 3) = (4 - 6) / 4 = -<span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">2</span><span class=\"den\">4</span></span> = -<span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">1</span><span class=\"den\">2</span></span><br>अतः अभीष्ट बिंदु P(x, y) = (-<span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">1</span><span class=\"den\">4</span></span>, -<span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">1</span><span class=\"den\">2</span></span>) है। Ans."
