          "answer": "त्रिभुज के केंद्रक का सूत्र है: P(x, y) = [ (x1+x2+x3)/3 , (y1+y2+y3)/3 ]<br>यहाँ x1=3, x2=-7, x3=10 और y1=-5, y2=4, y3=-2<br>x = (3 - 7 + 10) / 3 = <span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">6</span><span class=\"den\">3</span></span> = 2<br>y = (-5 + 4 - 2) / 3 = -<span class=\"frac\"><span class=\"num\">3</span><span class=\"den\">3</span></span> = -1<br>अतः केंद्रक का निर्देशांक (2, -1) होगा। Ans."
